column5: ISRG No relief in this thing

ISRG Im in for a halfposition now having patiently waited since last ER for 460 Were under the lower Bollinger band on the 2yr chart which is normally a VERY safe entry The lack of any plausible US endgame in its global tariff war is unquantifiable though and could lead to watershed declines But ISRG is a solid company and Im glad to add it to my portfolio
